sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant Popup as 📋 Popup UI
    participant CS as 📄 Content Script
    participant BG as ⚙️ Background SW
    participant API as 🔌 BobaAPIClient
    participant FastAPI as 🐳 FastAPI :7187
    participant GoSvc as 🐳 Go Service :7189
    participant qBit as ⬇️ qBitTorrent :8080

    Note over User,qBit: Single Torrent Send Flow

    User->>CS: Browse torrent site
    activate CS
    CS->>CS: MutationObserver detects<br/>magnet: link in DOM
    CS->>CS: parser.normalizeURL()
    CS->>BG: chrome.runtime.sendMessage<br/>{type: "DISCOVERED_TORRENTS", torrents}
    deactivate CS
    activate BG
    BG->>Popup: chrome.runtime.sendMessage<br/>{type: "UPDATE_POPUP", torrents}
    activate Popup
    Popup->>Popup: Render torrent list
    Popup-->>User: Show discovered torrents
    User->>Popup: Click "Send" button
    Popup->>BG: chrome.runtime.sendMessage<br/>{type: "SEND_TORRENT", torrent}
    deactivate Popup
    BG->>API: sendTorrent(torrent)
    activate API
    API->>API: Build request with auth headers<br/>X-Api-Key + Basic Auth
    par FastAPI Path
        API->>FastAPI: POST /api/torrents/add<br/>JSON body
        activate FastAPI
        FastAPI->>FastAPI: Validate torrent data
        FastAPI->>qBit: POST /api/v2/torrents/add<br/>form-data: urls, category
        activate qBit
        qBit->>qBit: Add to BitTorrent engine
        qBit-->>FastAPI: 200 OK + {hash}
        deactivate qBit
        FastAPI-->>API: 200 OK + {hash, status}
        deactivate FastAPI
    and Go Service Path
        API->>GoSvc: POST /api/torrents/add<br/>JSON body
        activate GoSvc
        GoSvc->>GoSvc: Validate + metadata lookup
        GoSvc->>qBit: POST /api/v2/torrents/add<br/>form-data
        activate qBit
        qBit->>qBit: Add to BitTorrent engine
        qBit-->>GoSvc: 200 OK + {hash}
        deactivate qBit
        GoSvc-->>API: 200 OK + {hash, status, metadata}
        deactivate GoSvc
    end
    API-->>BG: Promise resolved<br/>{success, hash, status}
    deactivate API
    BG->>BG: Store in send_history<br/>Update badge count
    BG->>Popup: chrome.runtime.sendMessage<br/>{type: "SEND_COMPLETE", result}
    activate Popup
    Popup-->>User: ✓ Notification: "Torrent added"
    deactivate Popup
    deactivate BG

    Note right of qBit: Alternative: magnet links are<br/>resolved via DHT for metadata
